## Required Annotations Per Endpoint

| HTTP Method | Required Annotations |
|-------------|---------------------|
| GET (single) | `@Operation`, `@ApiResponses` (200, 404), `@Parameter` |
| GET (list) | `@Operation` |
| POST | `@Operation`, `@ApiResponse` (201) |
| PUT | `@Operation`, `@ApiResponses` (200, 404), `@Parameter` |
| DELETE | `@Operation`, `@ApiResponses` (204, 404), `@Parameter` |

