## Checklist Before Generating Controller

- [ ] `@Tag` on class with name and description
- [ ] `@Operation` on every endpoint
- [ ] `@ApiResponses` for GET/PUT/DELETE endpoints
- [ ] `@ApiResponse` with 201 for POST endpoints
- [ ] `@Parameter` for all `@PathVariable` parameters
- [ ] `Page<T>` return type for list endpoints (not List<T>)
- [ ] `Pageable` parameter for list endpoints
- [ ] `@Valid` on all `@RequestBody` parameters
